divs: sighting detailswalking the dog before the storm moved in. noticed a bright star change color to amber then began to move west. retrieved family member to witness also then we counted at least 30 more star-like objects approaching from the east moving slowly to the west, without a definite pattern, some trailing behind others, some traveling in a triangle formation. when a plane passed by, some of the objects nearest to the plane dimmed, then brightened significantly after the plane passed (also moving west). camera wouldnt work, too dark for video. event happened for approx 1\2 hour, then storm clouds began to block ability to see event.
Summary: over 30 starlike objects moving from east to west just before storm clouds moved in from the west
Object Flight Path: Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path then hovering
